column5: East coast smelts with farm fresh eggs and coffee... Great way to start the weekend. What did everyone have for breaky?
Man, you overcooked those eggs!!  lol!
Good job I didn't share the pic of the toast! Heh heh
French toast for this french canadian.  Those smelt look good. I still have a bunch from the spring I need to eat.
This was my breakfast with eggs a few weekends back , it was a first time for me to have fish that time of day  , i never felt hungry again that day til late at night .... lol
Nope,cooked perfect,and if the toast was burnt,it was a well done breakfast.
Can't go wrong with that kinda breakfast Skipper.
